title: [Whistler's Pass]
description: The ear-splitting shriek of an unseen bird of prey echoes through the pass, the crooked beak from which it must have originated hidden among the dim stars above.  As the shrill cry slowly fades, the rocky cleft is once again masked in an eerie stillness.
